{"tid":657613,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【同遊沖繩再抵港】石原聰美新戀情曝光 熱戀SHOWROOM社長","createTime":"2018-05-08T09:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T12:20:58.000Z","uid":30001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f951b437c326eeebd22b24a37c370c3270c26f","tid":657613,"uid":30001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:11:45.000Z","msg":"31歲日本女星石原聰美與山下智久分手後，其感情生活即成坊間焦點。當山P搭上索模Niki並同遊夏威夷斷正後，仲以為石原聰美要到處散心，殊不知佢已火速有新歡，現任男友正是IT企業SHOWROOM嘅30歲社長前田裕二。<br />\n<br />\n據今期《週刊文春》報道，石原聰美在上月22日，偕前田裕二抵達沖繩石垣島，翌日再到竹富島入住當地高級渡假酒店，共度兩晚二人世界。雜誌向石原聰美事務所求證，發言人未有否認，只回應不會干涉石原聰美的私人時間。從今日公開嘅照片所見，石原聰美身上嘅小手袋，正是日前在旺角港鐵站被拍下時孭住嗰個，相信係上月底去沖繩再到香港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/171100_12358e9d5d1989e06985925b738f350b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F171100_12358e9d5d1989e06985925b738f350b.png&h=9ec0f1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180508/58167062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180508%2F58167062&d=LEs%2BwAtQgaw8rqlH5r8IfJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=11256402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180508%2F58167062&h=5c623fe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180508/58167062</a>"},{"pid":"c1bf35ec4b5a4ec788ac0ec339c7a3127c6b4953","tid":657613,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢終於可以令山p定性結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ace2e9e8fc8082035b471b698f4a070570b8cff","tid":657613,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"里美<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},